<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Task Dashboard</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: "Inter", "Noto Sans TC", "Microsoft JhengHei", sans-serif;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(0, 255, 156, 0.08), transparent 22%),
        radial-gradient(circle at bottom right, rgba(0, 255, 156, 0.05), transparent 18%),
        #111315;
    }

    .glass-panel {
      background: rgba(28, 31, 35, 0.92);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.28);
    }

    .grid-pattern {
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 28px 28px;
    }

    .neon-line {
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 255, 156, 0.35);
    }

    .status-dot {
      width: 10px;
      height: 10px;
      border-radius: 9999px;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    .task-row:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.24);
      border-color: rgba(0, 255, 156, 0.35);
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen text-zinc-100 overflow-x-hidden">
  <main class="relative min-h-screen px-6 py-10 md:px-10 lg:px-16">
    <!-- Decorative Shapes -->
    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute -top-16 -left-10 w-56 h-56 border border-emerald-400/20 rounded-full"></div>
      <div class="absolute top-20 right-10 w-40 h-40 border border-emerald-400/20 rotate-45"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-16 left-12 w-64 h-64 border border-white/5 rounded-3xl rotate-12"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-10 right-0 w-80 h-80 rounded-full bg-emerald-400/5 blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full grid-pattern opacity-40"></div>
    </div>

    <section class="relative mx-auto max-w-6xl">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="mb-10 flex flex-col gap-6 lg:flex-row lg:items-end lg:justify-between">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-3 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-emerald-400/30 bg-emerald-400/10 px-4 py-1 text-xs tracking-[0.3em] text-emerald-300 uppercase">
            <span class="status-dot bg-emerald-400"></span>
            Task Management
          </p>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white">任務清單頁面</h1>
          <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-sm md:text-base leading-7 text-zinc-400">
            以結構化資訊呈現 Priority、Task 與 Status，搭配深灰色系與亮色對比，打造專業、俐落且易讀的任務管理介面。
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass-panel rounded-2xl border border-white/10 px-5 py-4">
          <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-zinc-500">Overview</div>
          <div class="mt-3 flex gap-8">
            <div>
              <div class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">08</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-zinc-500">總任務</div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-2xl font-semibold text-emerald-300">03</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-zinc-500">進行中</div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-2xl font-semibold text-zinc-200">02</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-zinc-500">已完成</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Board -->
      <div class="glass-panel rounded-[28px] border border-white/10 overflow-hidden">
        <!-- Top Accent -->
        <div class="h-1.5 w-full bg-emerald-400 neon-line"></div>

        <!-- Table Header -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-4 border-b border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] px-5 py-4 md:px-7">
          <div class="col-span-3 md:col-span-2 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-emerald-300">Priority</div>
          <div class="col-span-5 md:col-span-7 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-zinc-300">Task</div>
          <div class="col-span-4 md:col-span-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-zinc-300">Status</div>
        </div>

        <!-- Rows -->
        <div class="p-4 md:p-5 space-y-4">
          <div class="task-row grid grid-cols-12 gap-4 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-zinc-900/60 px-5 py-5 transition duration-200 md:px-6">
            <div class="col-span-3 md:col-span-2 flex items-center">
              <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-red-400/30 bg-red-400/10 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-red-300">High</span>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-5 md:col-span-7 flex flex-col justify-center">
              <div class="text-base font-medium text-white">完成年度專案提案簡報</div>
              <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-zinc-500">整理內容架構、視覺設計與最終講稿</div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-4 md:col-span-3 flex items-center">
              <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-400/10 px-3 py-1.5 text-sm text-emerald-300">
                <span class="status-dot bg-emerald-400"></span>In Progress
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="task-row grid grid-cols-12 gap-4 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-zinc-900/60 px-5 py-5 transition duration-200 md:px-6">
            <div class="col-span-3 md:col-span-2 flex items-center">
              <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-yellow-400/30 bg-yellow-400/10 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-yellow-300">Medium</span>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-5 md:col-span-7 flex flex-col justify-center">
              <div class="text-base font-medium text-white">整理使用者研究訪談紀錄</div>
              <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-zinc-500">彙整關鍵洞察與痛點分類</div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-4 md:col-span-3 flex items-center">
              <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-zinc-800 px-3 py-1.5 text-sm text-zinc-300">
                <span class="status-dot bg-zinc-500"></span>Pending
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="task-row grid grid-cols-12 gap-4 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-zinc-900/60 px-5 py-5 transition duration-200 md:px-6">
            <div class="col-span-3 md:col-span-2 flex items-center">
              <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-emerald-400/30 bg-emerald-400/10 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-emerald-300">Low</span>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-5 md:col-span-7 flex flex-col justify-center">
              <div class="text-base font-medium text-white">更新團隊資料夾命名規範</div>
              <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-zinc-500">統一專案資料層級與檔名格式</div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-4 md:col-span-3 flex items-center">
              <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-zinc-100/10 px-3 py-1.5 text-sm text-zinc-200">
                <span class="status-dot bg-zinc-200"></span>Done
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="task-row grid grid-cols-12 gap-4 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-zinc-900/60 px-5 py-5 transition duration-200 md:px-6">
            <div class="col-span-3 md:col-span-2 flex items-center">
              <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-red-400/30 bg-red-400/10 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-red-300">High</span>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-5 md:col-span-7 flex flex-col justify-center">
              <div class="text-base font-medium text-white">確認首頁 UI 元件最終樣式</div>
              <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-zinc-500">按鈕、字體階層與色彩狀態確認</div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-4 md:col-span-3 flex items-center">
              <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-400/10 px-3 py-1.5 text-sm text-emerald-300">
                <span class="status-dot bg-emerald-400"></span>In Progress
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="task-row grid grid-cols-12 gap-4 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-zinc-900/60 px-5 py-5 transition duration-200 md:px-6">
            <div class="col-span-3 md:col-span-2 flex items-center">
              <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-yellow-400/30 bg-yellow-400/10 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-yellow-300">Medium</span>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-5 md:col-span-7 flex flex-col justify-center">
              <div class="text-base font-medium text-white">建立交付版本檢查清單</div>
              <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-zinc-500">上線前核對文案、圖片與互動細節</div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-4 md:col-span-3 flex items-center">
              <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-zinc-800 px-3 py-1.5 text-sm text-zinc-300">
                <span class="status-dot bg-zinc-500"></span>Pending
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="task-row grid grid-cols-12 gap-4 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-zinc-900/60 px-5 py-5 transition duration-200 md:px-6">
            <div class="col-span-3 md:col-span-2 flex items-center">
              <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border border-emerald-400/30 bg-emerald-400/10 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-emerald-300">Low</span>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-5 md:col-span-7 flex flex-col justify-center">
              <div class="text-base font-medium text-white">整理會議紀要與待辦事項</div>
              <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-zinc-500">補齊決議內容並同步團隊</div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-4 md:col-span-3 flex items-center">
              <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-zinc-100/10 px-3 py-1.5 text-sm text-zinc-200">
                <span class="status-dot bg-zinc-200"></span>Done
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
